![](Images/AРМІЯINFORM/2023-04-07T92-00-00-04-00/foto-3-2-1-e1680888448329.jpg)The third significant challenge is the increase in the number of citizens who are poverty.Another line of negative impact of demographic changes on the social protection system is the rapid disability of society. According to the Pension Fund system, which registers the payments of disability pensions, during 2022, 13 thousand people began to receive a disability pension.

